X_recombinant_lineage: 3. The writing order of the two lineages listed in "mostly_identified_parents" is independent of the genome position of SARS-CoV-2.
4. "mostly_identified_parents" means the identified parental lineages for most of the recombinants.
5. The "acknowledge_parents" for each recombination lineage is downloaded from https://github.com/cov-lineages/pango-designation/blob/master/pango_designation/alias_key.json on Mar 28, 2023.
6. The transformation for parts of lineages' abbreviation is referenced from https://github.com/cov-lineages/pango-designation/blob/master/lineage_notes.txt on Mar 28, 2023.
